OL,3,CHousehold water bills to rise by an
OL,4,Caverage of 5.4% from April
OL,6,FHousehold water bills across England
OL,7,Fand Wales will rise by an average of
OL,8,F5.4% from April, the industry has
OL,9,Fconfirmed.
OL,11,FThe increase ` which equates to #33 a
OL,12,Fyear for the average household ` is
OL,13,Ftwo percentage points above inflation
OL,14,Fbut comes as companies prepare to
OL,15,Finvest #20 billion over 2026-27 to
OL,16,Fsecure water supplies and end sewage
OL,17,Fentering rivers and seas, Water UK
OL,18,Fsaid.
