OL,3,CHousehold water bills to rise by an
OL,4,Caverage of 5.4% from April
OL,6,FThere has been ongoing public anger
OL,7,Fabout the amount of sewage being
OL,8,Freleased into waterways, exacerbated
OL,9,Fby firms increasing bills to pay for
OL,10,Fupgrades after decades of
OL,11,Funderinvestment.
OL,13,FOfwat has allowed water firms to put
OL,14,Fup bills by 36% between 2025 and 2030,
OL,15,Fwith most of that ` 20% or an average
OL,16,F#86 ` front-loaded on to last April's
OL,17,Fannual rise.
