OL,6,FSouth East Water is raising bills by
OL,7,Fan average 7% to #324 a year after its
OL,8,Fcustomers suffered days of supply
OL,9,Fdisruption this month, blamed on Storm
OL,10,FGoretti, causing burst pipes and power
OL,11,Fcuts, following a similar incident the
OL,12,Fprevious month when 24,000 people in
OL,13,FTunbridge Wells were left without
OL,14,Fdrinking water for two weeks.
OL,16,FWater UK said the cash raised from
OL,17,Fwater bills could only be used to fund
OL,18,Finfrastructure that had been
OL,19,Findependently determined to be "new,
OL,20,Fnecessary and value for money".
